Annex B: Contact Points to Seek Support for Quitting

Social Service Agency: WE CARE Community Services
Type of Services:
- Counselling (individual and group)
- Drop-in recovery centre
- Peer-support and recovery groups
- Group therapy programmes (CBT-based, relapse prevention, emotional regulation)
- Workshops and educational talks
Contact:
- Tel: 3165 8017  
- WhatsApp: 8391 3023  
- Email: help@wecare.org.sg  
- Website: https://www.wecare.org.sg/

---

Social Service Agency: Singapore Anti-Narcotics Association (SANA)
Type of Services:
- Step-Up Centres
  • Walk-in facilities supporting individuals in recovery from drug misuse.  
  • Provide a safe environment for reintegration and building social support.  
  • Open to recovering persons, their families, and those seeking help.  

- Case Management Services
  • Interim financial assistance.  
  • Casework and counselling for stabilisation.  

- Psychotherapy
  • Evidence-based therapeutic interventions (e.g., CBT, trauma-informed approaches).  
  • Addresses co-occurring mental health conditions, behavioural challenges, and relapse risk factors.  

Contact:
- Tel: 6732 1122  
- Email: sana@sana.org.sg  
- Website: https://www.sana.org.sg/

---

Healthcare Institution: Institute of Mental Health (IMH)
Service: National Addiction Management Services (NAMS)
Type of Services:
- Comprehensive addiction assessment (clinical + psychosocial)
- Treatment for substance-related and behavioural addictions
- Individual therapy, group therapy, and family therapy
- Integrated care for co-existing mental health conditions (e.g. anxiety, depression)
- Professional relapse prevention planning
Contact:
- Appointments: 6389 2200  
- Online form: https://for.sg/nams-appointment-form  
- Website: https://www.nams.sg
